data.description: We are proud to present this turn-key remodeled, easy-access ground-floor condo in the popular Finisterra on the Lake Community in Mission Viejo. Some amenities include a private community beach, a sparkling pool, a private fishing area, and access to Mission Viejo Lake amenities.   The Finisterra Lake community boasts views of the Saddleback Mountains, a truly rare find in this area. Get ready to be inspired, as these breathtaking views complement the upscale interior finishes. This two-bedroom, two-bathroom unit has recently undergone updated renovations, with new modern kitchen and bathroom designs.  This home is brimming with recent upgrades that include a custom kitchen with recessed lighting, beautiful freshly painted walls, new white Quartz countertops with gray veining, 3D Subway tile backsplash, sleek modern stainless-steel handles, and state-of-the-art stainless-steel appliances.  The bathrooms shine with bright new finishes, glass enclosures, shower tiling, and flooring. Easy-to-care-for Shaw carpet has been installed that is easy to upkeep and has accessibility features.   Luxurious travertine flooring seamlessly flows through the entry, kitchen, and dining room.   The spacious Master bedroom has been repainted and is also carpeted.  The master bathroom has a new dual-sink vanity with updated sinks, fixtures, and countertops. The master has a generous walk-in closet. The guest room has been repainted and carpeted and the guest bathroom also has beautiful travertine flooring and updated counters, sinks, fixtures, and shower.  The garage is located near the front door of your new home. The magnificence extends beyond the interior, with equally stunning views from the primary bedroom, kitchen, living room, and entryway.  The private balcony is conveniently connected to the living room and primary bedroom for easy access. Come view this beautiful, renovated masterpiece, it will sell fast!
